# 🚀 Full Stack Authentication System

A complete full-stack web application that provides secure user authentication using modern web technologies. This project demonstrates real-world development including backend APIs, database integration, and deployment.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

* 🔗 Frontend: https://your-site.netlify.app
* 🔗 Backend: https://intership13.onrender.com

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
* **Database:** MySQL (Railway Cloud)
* **Authentication:** JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
* **Deployment:**

  * Frontend → Netlify
  * Backend → Render

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 User Signup & Login
* 🔑 Secure password hashing using bcrypt
* 🎫 JWT-based authentication
* 📊 Protected dashboard route
* 🌐 Fully deployed live project
* 🎨 Clean and modern UI

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
project/
 ├── backend/
 │     ├── server.js
 │     ├── package.json
 │     ├── .gitignore
 │     └── .env (not included in repository)
 │
 └── frontend/
       ├── home.html
       ├── index.html
       ├── signup.html
       ├── dashboard.html
       ├── style.css
       └── script.js
```

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions (Local)

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git
cd your-repo
```

---

### 2️⃣ Backend Setup

```
cd backend
npm install
```

Create a `.env` file inside the backend folder:

```
MYSQL_URL=your_mysql_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
```

Run the server:

```
node server.js
```

---

### 3️⃣ Frontend Setup

Simply open `home.html` in your browser.

---

## 🧱 Database Schema

```
CREATE TABLE users (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  email VARCHAR(255),
  password VARCHAR(255)
);
```

---

## 🚀 Deployment

* Frontend hosted on Netlify
* Backend hosted on Render
* MySQL database hosted on Railway

---

## 🔐 Security

Sensitive data such as database credentials and JWT secrets are stored using environment variables and are not exposed in the repository.

